{"tid":1148532,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"搭地鐵最唔想邊類人企係你既周圍？","createTime":"2019-05-10T13:57:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-10T21:22:49.000Z","uid":130303,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"05c3bebaec7c904b4d579858edc483063cdfa7ca","tid":1148532,"uid":130303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T13:57:32.000Z","msg":"話說今日放工時間係荔景出，有個呀婆未到站已經企咗係門口位等出<br />\n車門一開閘，佢行出一步，然後竟然<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n停咗係度，我係佢後面係俾佢擋住，行唔到，側邊又有人，心入面真係好想話個呀婆阻住人行，WTF"},{"pid":"f10c4bb86751d1f875e22101db7164aacad79d8c","tid":1148532,"uid":124256,"like":45,"dislike":0,"score":45,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T14:01:37.000Z","msg":"女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔小心掂到佢隨時監都有得坐"},{"pid":"82d192c26880f26cf42cabad499d7cb9fc78ea12","tid":1148532,"uid":103948,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T14:02:35.000Z","msg":"有咖哩味果啲"},{"pid":"715ab3098b8d5fb67d741aba8652435ecb7a6d4f","tid":1148532,"uid":21395,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T14:02:47.000Z","msg":"臭狐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b95ff2db622df677250e2901ebd6c5988a8c8a6","tid":1148532,"uid":189234,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T14:03:12.000Z","msg":"唔熟嘅朋友"},{"pid":"9a418ac61802d47df05bc493e455753444a78599","tid":1148532,"uid":13084,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T14:03:51.000Z","msg":"咳鬼"},{"pid":"639c54e421e633c13d00f23757e3e56e6a71e21a","tid":1148532,"uid":212845,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T14:04:53.000Z","msg":"流汗有臭狐嘅阿叔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咪撚癡埋嚟"},{"pid":"3eca5e2d35e3bd54df574d57ba387579109607aa","tid":1148532,"uid":188493,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T14:06:12.000Z","msg":"死煙剷"},{"pid":"1d378a514e730c4ef191dd7e96e669195144db5c","tid":